"title": "8805: pride, results of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8805",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The real nature of pride can be seen in the fact that it leads to many other evils and ends in destruction.</p>\n<h2>Pride leads to other forms of evil</h2>\n<h3>Self-deception</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:3\">GAL 6:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:17-Deut8:18\">DEU 8:17–8:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa16:6\">ISA 16:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa47:10\">ISA 47:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:16\">JER 49:16</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:3\">OBA 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor8:2\">1CO 8:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:3-1Tim6:4\">1TI 6:3–6:4</a></p>\n<h3>Spiritual blindness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer43:2\">JER 43:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:14\">DEU 8:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:16\">NEH 9:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:29\">NEH 9:29</a></p>\n<h3>A hard heart</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps36:2\">PSA 36:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:3\">PSA 10:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps52:1\">PSA 52:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:20\">DAN 5:20</a></p>\n<h3>A malicious spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:85\">PSA 119:85</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:8\">PSA 73:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps140:5\">PSA 140:5</a></p>\n<h3>Contempt for others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps123:4\">PSA 123:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:51\">PSA 119:51</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:24\">PRO 21:24</a></p>\n<h3>Quarrelling</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:10\">PRO 13:10</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Violence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:6\">PSA 73:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth3:5-Esth3:6\">EST 3:5–3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:14\">PSA 86:14</a></p>\n<h3>Injustice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:78\">PSA 119:78</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps56:2\">PSA 56:2</a></p>\n<h3>Oppression</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:2\">PSA 10:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:122\">PSA 119:122</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:4-Hab2:5\">HAB 2:4–2:5</a></p>\n<h3>Contempt for God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:4\">PSA 10:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:22\">2KI 19:22</a></p>\n<h2>Pride may be accompanied by temporary prosperity</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:3\">PSA 73:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:5\">PSA 10:5</a></p>\n<h2>Pride ends in disaster</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:5\">PRO 16:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:18\">PRO 16:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:28\">2SA 22:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:27\">PSA 18:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job40:11-Job40:12\">JOB 40:11–40:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:23\">PSA 31:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps101:5\">PSA 101:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:2\">PRO 11:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:25\">PRO 15:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:12\">PRO 26:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:23\">PRO 29:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:11-Isa2:12\">ISA 2:11–2:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:17\">ISA 2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:11\">ISA 13:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:5\">ISA 26:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:11\">ZEP 3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal4:1\">MAL 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:51-Luke1:52\">LUK 1:51–1:52</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:6\">1TI 3:6</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of the proud being humbled</h2>\n<p>Pharaoh:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:28\">EXO 14:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:10\">NEH 9:10</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:16\">2CH 26:16</a> <em>Uzziah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:21\">2CH 32:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:12\">ISA 10:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:16\">ISA 10:16</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:25\">2CH 32:25</a> <em>Hezekiah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth7:10\">EST 7:10</a> <em>Haman</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:16-Isa3:17\">ISA 3:16–3:17</a> <em>the women of Zion</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:19\">ISA 13:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:11-Isa14:15\">ISA 14:11–14:15</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa23:9\">ISA 23:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:10-Isa25:12\">ISA 25:10–25:12</a> <em>Moab</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:1-Isa28:3\">ISA 28:1–28:3</a> <em>Samaria</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa47:10-Isa47:11\">ISA 47:10–47:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:31-Jer50:32\">JER 50:31–50:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer13:9\">JER 13:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek7:24\">EZK 7:24</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:49-Ezek16:50\">EZK 16:49–16:50</a> <em>Sodom</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:5-Ezek28:9\">EZK 28:5–28:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:17\">EZK 28:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek30:6\">EZK 30:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek32:12\">EZK 32:12</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:30-Dan4:33\">DAN 4:30–4:33</a> <em>Nebuchadnezzar</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:30\">DAN 5:30</a> <em>Belshazzar</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos6:8\">AMO 6:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph2:15\">ZEP 2:15</a> <em>Nineveh</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:6\">ZEC 9:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech10:11\">ZEC 10:11</a> <em>Assyria</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:23\">MAT 11:23</a> <em>Capernaum</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:21-Acts12:23\">ACT 12:21–12:23</a> <em>Herod</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:7-Rev18:8\">REV 18:7–18:8</a> <em>Babylon the Great</em></p>",
